{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, research LLM can be an additional tool to provide theoretical answers and formulate published recommendations [114].",
    "These components continue the work of the LLM and include communication skills, language therapy, and writing and language support.",
    "Incorporating these tools into the LLM can reduce enrollment by reducing barriers to entry into higher education.",
    "The authors of [115] explain that LLM translation and remediation programs can increase the integrity of education by supporting students who do not speak English.",
    "This is especially helpful for students whose families lack English skills."
  ]
}